  The  Government  has  no  intention  to 

undermine  the  Parliamentary  democracy.    This  Bill is  for  introduction  and this is 

the procedure.  This is the prerogative of Hon. Speaker.  There is a provision in this 

regard in Business Rules and this is the right of the Government. 

The Bill was introduced. 

 

 

